10/extras/d215c373e7e1585062bd74375f2dcfb2.mp4?t=1628498556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>·Puzzles at the right difficulty and thought-provoking riddles to provide you with such a smooth ride you’ll never get bored in this world.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093910/extras/b203f18c1d1dc9e0f60d0956db722657.poster.avif?t=1628498556\" width=616 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093910/extras/b203f18c1d1dc9e0f60d0956db722657.webm?t=1628498556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1093910/extras/b203f18c1d1dc9e0f60d0956db722657.mp4?t=1628498556\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>·With so many Easter Eggs and bonuses scattered around Kuromori-chō, we invite you to discover them all! They might just make your day.<br><br>English subtitles proofread by woosk from Visual novel, JRPG, Anime and partner website Sinical Network.",
